  <brief_title>A Medical Research Study to Evaluate the Effects of ACT-246475 in Adults With Heart Attack</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Open-label, Randomized, Study to Assess the Onset of Platelet Aggregation Inhibition After a Single Subcutaneous Injection of ACT-246475 in Adults With Acute Myocardial Infarction</official_title>
