  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study is to find out how fast a drug called ACT-246475 can prevent platelets
      from binding together. This study will also help to find out more about the safety of this
      new drug. The drug ACT-246475 will be used in 2 different doses (8 mg or 16 mg) and will be
      administered in the thigh.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
